name: Yoda, Senior Council Member (V) (AI)
Lore: 'Senior Jedi Council member. Responsible for the early training of Obi-Wan Kenobi. When Qui-Gon brought Anakin before the Council, Yoda voted not to train the boy.',
Text: 'Deploys only to [Episode I] sites. While at Jedi Council Chamber, immune to attrition, Jedi are deploy -2 here, and (unless a Dark Jedi here) other Jedi may treat ''Jedi Council Chamber'' in their game text as ''[Episode I] battleground sites.''(Original concept by Jacob Taylor - PC Volunteer Award 2005)',
